author: Kate Taylor
description: Starbucks quietly had all US employee embark on a new customer service initiative. However, some baristas say that the new agenda is hurting the coffee giant.
title: Starbucks is quietly changing the business as furious baristas slam the 'cult that pays $9 an hour'

author: Ashley Carman
description: My day starts at 7AM. I get up, brush my teeth, throw on tinted SPF moisturizer, and leave my Queens, New York apartment by, ideally, 7:30. My usual first stop is the Starbucks next to my subway...
title: I've discovered the magic of ordering ahead at Starbucks, and all the guilt that comes with it
